    "description": {
      "value": "<p>A more advanced version of Shoton: Rokkaku Shuriken, this technique creates a large shuriken, which is hurled at his opponent. The user makes a ranged attack roll with the thrown weapon at his highest attack bonus for each shuriken, dealing 2d8 points of slashing damage plus the user's strength modifier on a successful hit. The shuriken created by this technique dissolve into shimmering, fragments of crystal at the end of the round.</p>\n\n<hr><p><b>Requires:</b> Shoton: Rokkaku Shuriken (3)</p>\n<p><b>Effect:</b> Creates a large-sized shuriken</p>\n",
